articles.author: Al Jazeera
articles.title: Russian and US crew blasts off in Soyuz rocket bound for ISS - Al Jazeera
articles.description: The spacecraft with two Russian and one American astronaut took off from the Baikonur Cosmodrome in Kazakhstan.
articles.content:
A Russian rocket carrying a crew from the United States and Russia has docked with the International Space Station (ISS).
